{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ready Player One, Film dengan Nuansa Pop Culture yang Kental","content":"<p>Oleh: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/helloditta/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@Helloditta</a></p>\n<p>Kalau kalian suka sama <em>pop culture </em>dari mulai tahun 80an, sudah pasti bakal suka sama film baru tayang ini, judulnya &#8220;<em>Ready Player One</em>&#8220;! Film yang diangkat dari novel berjudul sama karangan Ernest Cline ini menyimpan banyak sekali <em>easter egg</em> dari <em>pop culture</em>! Ada <em>easter egg </em>dan referensi dari musik, <em>game</em>, film, tv <em>series</em> dan buku!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45396\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45396\" data-attachment-id=\"45396\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/attachment/rposekian/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rposekian.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: Youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rposekian-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rposekian.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45396\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rposekian.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rposekian.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rposekian-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45396\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Ceritanya sendiri mengambil latar di tahun 2045, di mana masyarakatnya menjadi <em>Dystophia. </em>Banyak orang menghabiskan waktu mereka untuk <em>online</em> di suatu tempat bernama OASIS melalui sebuah perangkat <em>Virtual Reality</em>. Di mana kita bisa menjadi apapun yang kita inginkan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45387\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45387\" data-attachment-id=\"45387\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/attachment/rpo2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45387\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo2.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45387\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>OASIS diciptakan oleh James Halliday. yang saat meninggal menyebarkan video wasiat bahwa dia meninggalkan sebuah <em>treasure hunt</em> di OASIS. Nah, jika ada yang berhasil menyelesaikan 3 <em>game</em> utamanya, maka dia berhak mendapatkan seluruh warisan James Halliday.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45389\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45389\" data-attachment-id=\"45389\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/attachment/rpo4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45389\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45389\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Film ini dibintangi oleh Tye Sheridan yang berperan sebagai Wade Watts, seorang anak yang tinggal di perkampungan kumuh bersama adik dari ibunya. Gak heran kalau dia sangat kecanduan pada OASIS. Saat <em>log in</em> ke OASIS, dia memiliki avatar bernama &#8220;Parzival&#8221;.</p>\n<p>Di OASIS dia berteman dengan <em>player</em> bernama &#8220;Ache&#8221;. Gak hanya itu, dia juga bertemu <em>player</em> perempuan dengan <em>nickname</em> &#8220;Art3mis&#8221;. Ada juga dua <em>player</em> lain dengan <em>nickname</em> &#8220;Sho&#8221; dan &#8220;Daito&#8221; yang juga bergabung bersama Wade.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45390\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45390\" data-attachment-id=\"45390\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/attachment/rpo5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.esquire.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.esquire.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45390\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.esquire.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45390\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.esquire.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Wade atau Parzival dengan teman-temannya menjadi <em>Gunter </em>atau pemburu harta karun dengan memainkan <em>games</em> di OASIS. Mereka mencoba memecahkan berbagai petunjuk yang ditinggalkan James Halliway di setiap <em>game</em>.</p>\n<p>Sayangnya, ada sebuah perusahaan bernama IOI (<em>Innovative Online Industry</em>) yang dipimpin Nolan Sorrento (Ben Mendelsohn). Dia berusaha dengan berbagai cara curang, hingga mengancam dan menggagalkan Wade dan timnya mendapatkan harta karun itu.</p>\n<p>OASIS diciptakan dengan banyak refrensi <em>pop culture</em> dari masa kecil Halliday. Jadi buat kalian yang suka banget <em>pop culture,</em> sudah pasti bakal seneng banget deh nostalgia masa kecil lewat film, ini!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45386\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45386\" data-attachment-id=\"45386\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/attachment/rpo1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45386\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45386\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Hampir sebagian besar film ini mengambil latar di OASIS dibanding di dunia nyata. Tapi tetap enggak mengurangi kerennya film ini. Soalnya setiap <em>scene</em> disuguhi banyak sekali refrensi <em>pop culture</em>!</p>\n<p>Seperti motor Akira dari anime &#8220;Akira&#8221; yang dipakai oleh &#8220;Art3mis&#8221;, juga mobil <em>DeLorean time machine </em>dari &#8220;<em>back to the future&#8221;</em> yang dipakai oleh Parzival. Sebenarnya sejak tahun lalu, sudah banyak <em>pop culture easter egg</em> yang dikasih lihat di <em>trailer</em> filmnya saat muncul.  Tapi di filmnya, kamu akan dapat lebih banyak lagi!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45388\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45388\" data-attachment-id=\"45388\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ready-player-one-film-dengan-nuansa-pop-culture-yang-kental/attachment/rpo3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: youtube.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45388\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: youtube.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/rpo3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45388\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: youtube.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Psst, bukan cuma <em>pop culture</em> dari tahun 80-an, loh! Ada juga banyak <em>pop culture</em> dari jaman sekarang. Seperti karakter dari <em>game</em> &#8220;<em>Overwatch</em>&#8220;! Film Spielberg ini memang sejak awal banyak menarik minat para penonton. Kemunculan karakter <em>video game</em> yang cukup banyak, menjadi gaya tarik tersendiri.  Sejauh ini &#8220;<em>Ready Player One</em>&#8221; berhasil membawa banyak pesan bagus serta eksekusi visual yang luar biasa.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/cSp1dM2Vj48\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>So, tunggu apalagi? Yuk, cari banyak <em>easter egg</em> di &#8220;<em>Ready Player One</em>&#8220;! Filmnya ini sudah mulai rilis di Indonesia dari tanggal 28 Maret 2018. Jadi sudah siap masuk ke OASIS?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"2a7495c1-2eb2-51da-9eae-85ffda766409"}}}